title: Howard Stern Presents Anthrax
description:
Howard Stern Presents Anthrax  (49:13)

Thrash metal legend and Stern Show super fan Scott Ian shares his history of the band, stories behind the concert, and his admiration for all things Howard Stern. You'll hear the classic songs and more all recorded live in Japan from last year's Loud Park Festival.

* A.I.R.
* Madhouse.
* Caught In A Mosh.
* Antisocial.
* Got The Time.
* I'm The Man.
* Indians.
* Among The Living
